{"tid":1514708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"將軍澳再現持刀漢 警搜捕5小時拉涉案中年男","createTime":"2019-08-29T00:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T00:52:51.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64adb6a0e300af1249aa84a910853f3c38c0aaab","tid":1514708,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T00:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oggUs0FCTHjrBsRKiereYg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-08/80fc8e80-c9f0-11e9-8fe6-b80a345181e5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FoggUs0FCTHjrBsRKiereYg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-08%2F80fc8e80-c9f0-11e9-8fe6-b80a345181e5&h=ccd64c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本月20日凌晨將軍澳寶順路連儂牆發生斬人案，釀成3男女受傷，其中一名女記者慘被斬至重傷，涉案疑兇被捕，事件弄得將軍澳居民人心惶惶。昨(28日)晚接近11時，尚德邨商場外有一批街坊聚集叫口號，期間在場人士察覺一名操內地口音男子，拿着一個紅色背心膠袋，袋內疑似藏有利刀；在場街坊上前了解，有人更亮出一把軍刀揮舞，繼而趁亂跑進廣隆閣乘升降機登樓，目擊街坊不敢貿然尾隨。<br />\n<br />\n據消息稱，目擊疑人上樓的街坊，遂向大廈保安員求助，經翻查閉路電視片段，懷疑持刀漢乘升降機抵達37樓後步出升降機外，隨即報警求助。由於上周二區內發生連儂牆傷人案，兇徒犯案後一度逃回住所，事件引起軒然大波，故再驚現持刀漢，惹來大批街坊關注及到場了解，而警方接報後大為緊張，派出多名警員登樓搜索。<br />\n<br />\n至近凌晨4時，警員經逐家逐戶拍門查看，終在其中一單位尋獲持刀男子，並在單位檢獲涉案軍刀。據了解，涉案男子50歲，與家人同住，患有情緒病，他半夜睡醒，驚覺家人不在單位內，思前想後，擔心家人有事，遂在家中擸刀後外出周圍「尋親」，期間被街坊發現他眼神迷惘，並一度亮出軍刀揮舞，幸無傷人，他涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器被警方拘捕，蒙頭帶署調查，案中軍刀亦檢走查驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AN2AT5a7LujJSzdlCalvfw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-08/ae295870-c9f0-11e9-bfaf-6303e18e2154\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAN2AT5a7LujJSzdlCalvfw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-08%2Fae295870-c9f0-11e9-bfaf-6303e18e2154&h=e6f04f31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb62759cecb110c091fe2bb2131a94ef54195830","tid":1514708,"uid":3109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T00:29:08.000Z","msg":"做戲姐，想補鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e90773428778c6da625fe493e3e5dd5f6716007","tid":1514708,"uid":74155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T00:33:42.000Z","msg":"古有擸刀開生果<br />\n今有擸刀尋親<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48029be93898024cb017fc99d489fa23a62a214","tid":1514708,"uid":200070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T00:52:51.000Z","msg":"呢頭拉 可能果頭放<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後仲可能未必起訴<br />\n不過就呃到人以為黑社會肯做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}